            </TextBlock>
        </Label>

        <Label Width="280" Height="60"
               HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Top" Margin="20,50,0,0"
               Foreground="White">
            <TextBlock>
                Student at <Bold>Transylvania University of Brasov</Bold>,<LineBreak/>
                Faculty of Mathematics and Computer Science,<LineBreak/>
                <Bold>Applied Computer Science</Bold> (10LF361).
            </TextBlock>
        </Label>

    </Grid>
</Window>
